威尔·法瑞尔不明白跨性别恐惧症：“你为什么要关心别人是否幸福？为什么这会威胁到你？” https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-ferrell-doesnt-understand-transphobia-why-would-you-care-if-somebodys-happy-why-is-that-throne-to-you- 3797728?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=will-ferrell-不明白-跨性别恐惧症-为什么你会关心如果有人快乐为什么对你有威胁Elizabeth AubreyFri, 27 Sep 2024 13:48:08 +0000 Film NewsNews..Netflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3797728 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="威尔·法瑞尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我认为我们害怕我们不知道的东西”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-ferrell-doesnt-understand-transphobia-why-would-you-care-if-somebodys-happy-why-is-that-threatening-to-you-3797728">威尔·法雷尔 (Will Ferrell) 的帖子不理解跨性别恐惧症：“你为什么要关心别人是否幸福？为什么这会威胁到你？”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="威尔·法瑞尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Will-Ferrell-Photo-by-Jeremy-Chan_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-ferrell">威尔·法雷尔</a>表示他不理解跨性别者恐惧症，并问道：“你为什么要关心别人是否幸福？为什么这会威胁到你？”</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/snl-best-music-performances-2431631"><em>SNL</em>英雄：您最喜爱的明星在<em>周六夜现场的</em>精彩表演</a></strong></li></ul><p>费雷尔在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>纪录片<i>《威尔与哈珀》</i>新闻发布会上接受了<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/will-ferrell-harper-steele-netflix-b2618823.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《独立报》</i></a>采访，该纪录片重点讲述了费雷尔和哈珀·斯蒂尔之间的友谊。两人于 90 年代在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/saturday-night-live"><i>《周六夜现场》</i></a>中相识，在他们的友谊 30 年后，斯蒂尔公开承认自己是跨性别者。</p><p>这部纪录片于今年早些时候在圣丹斯电影节首映，讲述了斯蒂尔变性后这两个朋友穿越美国的公路旅行。</p><p>当被问及他对跨性别恐惧症为何存在的看法时，费雷尔回答道：“我认为我们害怕我们不知道的东西。</p><p> “那里有仇恨。这是非常真实的，在某些情况下对跨性别者来说非常不安全……但我不知道为什么跨性别者要威胁我作为一个顺性男性。我不知道哈珀为什么要威胁我。”</p><p>他继续说道：“这对我来说太奇怪了，因为哈珀终于……<i>她</i>……她终于成为了她本来就应该成为的人。不管你最终是否能理解这一点，你为什么要关心别人是否幸福呢？为什么这对你构成威胁？如果跨性别群体对你构成威胁，我认为这源于对自己不自信或不安全。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="威尔和哈珀 |官方预告片| Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PRZ1ELeGepo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>费雷尔此前曾在纪录片首映前夕在圣丹斯电影节接受<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/will-ferrell-transgender-community-sundance-documentary-1235881250/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《综艺》</i></a>采访，并解释说斯蒂尔在发给几位朋友的电子邮件中公开了自己的跨性别身份。</p><p> “我们所有人都非常支持并表达了爱……但这引发了一些问题，比如我们可以如何帮助你？需要我们做什么？”他告诉媒体。</p><p>费雷尔表示，在斯蒂尔向他出柜之前，他对跨性别群体“零了解”。他解释说：“我遇到过跨性别者，但我的生活中没有任何人。所以这对我来说是全新的领域，这就是为什么我认为这部电影对我们来说是如此令人兴奋，可以在世界范围内上映。这是我们所有独联体社区中的人能够提出问题、倾听并作为朋友讨论这一旅程的机会。” </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/will-ferrell-expresses-regret-for-dressing-up-as-a-woman-on-snl-3792576"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/will-ferrell-to-play-benefit-show-with-swedish-house-mafia-in-chicago-3774689">Ferrell 将于下个月在芝加哥与瑞典 House Mafia 一起担任 DJ，</a>以帮助<a href="https://cancerforcollege.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cancer For College</a> 。</p><p> <i>《威尔与哈珀》</i>现已在 Netflix 上播出。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-ferrell-doesnt-understand-transphobia-why-would-you-care-if-somebodys-happy-why-is-that-threatening-to-you-3797728">威尔·法雷尔 (Will Ferrell) 的帖子不理解跨性别恐惧症：“你为什么要关心别人是否幸福？为什么这会威胁到你？”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
